com.nokia.midp.examples.location.golf
Class GolfHelperMIDlet

java.lang.Object
  javax.microedition.midlet.MIDlet
      com.nokia.midp.examples.location.golf.GolfHelperMIDlet
public class GolfHelperMIDlet
extends javax.microedition.midlet.MIDlet

This class illustrates the implementation of a simple MIDlet to demonstrate the use of JSR-179 the location API.

This class extends the class javax.microedition.midlet.MIDlet. It creates and maintains references to a LocationScreen object and a HoleSelector object.

Note that the class has no defined constructor.
